column1: #Text=Make Food That Will Help Fight Lead Exposure
#Text=Lead exposure can be prevented by changing your diet and consuming 3 important nutrients everyday .
#Text=Calcium , Vitamin C , and Iron are key nutrients to help prevent lead exposure .
#Text=Calcium strengthens bones , which makes it less likely for lead to be absorbed .
#Text=Vitamin C helps your kidneys get rid of lead .
#Text=Calcium and Vitamin C , along with Iron can prevent lead from being absorbed into your body .
#Text=The specific foods listed below contain these nutrients .
#Text=Consuming small meals like these throughout the day can ensure that you 're receiving enough of these nutrients .
#Text=Mix 1 egg , 1 teaspoon of vanilla extract , and ½ a teaspoon of cinnamon into a bowl
#Text=Dip bread into the mixture , coating both sides evenly
#Text=Cook bread slices on medium heat until both sides are browned
#Text=OPTIONAL : Serve with maple syrup or top it off with banana slices or any other fruit as they provide Vitamin C and other beneficial nutrients .
#Text=Slice open a bagel and place it on a pan .
#Text=Spread 2 tablespoons of tomato sauce onto the bagels
#Text=Add shredded cheese ( or a cheese slice ) onto each bagel .
#Text=OPTIONAL : Add toppings such as pepperoni for taste .
#Text=Any lean meat is also great source for iron .
#Text=Bake in oven for 10 minutes or until cheese is melted
#Text=Add 2 cups of frozen strawberries and 1 peeled banana into a blender .
#Text=It 's best to cut the tops of the strawberries first .
#Text=Add one cup of milk ( almond is preferred ) and one cup of ice .
#Text=The ice makes for a thicker smoothie .
#Text=Milk is an excellent source of calcium and strengthens bones .
#Text=add a dollop of yogurt ( another source of Vitamin C ) or a tablespoon of honey for taste
#Text=Pulse in blender until all ingredients are combined
#Text=Do n't add all ingredients for the smoothie at once , or else they may get stuck .
#Text=Try adding in the ice after blending the fruit and milk if this happens .
#Text=Be sure to watch the bottom of bagels to make sure they do n't burn .
#Text=Watch out for the blender blade and make sure to keep lid on when pulsing the blender .
#Text=Do n't grease the pan for the french toast too much .
#Text=Yogurts and fruits are rich in Vitamin C
#Text=Milk and cheese are a great source in Calcium
